s=\"review-title\">Good Plugin, my website look good and load faster after use this plugin.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdshopper\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aa39f7f7ef9420fbb8f39a657c56cdfc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aa39f7f7ef9420fbb8f39a657c56cdfc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdshopper\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mdshopper</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Easy set up and simple to use! Great result of picture optimization with direct speed - page load result, even in the free version.\nThanks</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">cff are awesome</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nashaweb100\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/308b75b065bcf49266e18e334d5f19a0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/308b75b065bcf49266e18e334d5f19a0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nashaweb100\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nashaweb100</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been creating a quite tricky calculations form, and ofcourse I got stuck, and the great people in cff answered my questions immediately and I\'ve solved all the problems.  \nTheir prices are really good and they don\'t charge for extra after you are finished, like some other plugins.\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great! one of the best plugins i have ever used</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/micheal-oluoch\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/56e5d162d5eabb145a1b8e3711e413c0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/56e5d162d5eabb145a1b8e3711e413c0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/micheal-oluoch\" class=\"reviewer-name\">micheal Oluoch</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 8, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great! one of the best plugins I have ever used</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">great simple to use!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/claudia82\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7eeb8efdce1f34c8f2b0612ace7fed11?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7eeb8efdce1f34c8f2b0612ace7fed11?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/claudia82\" class=\"reviewer-name\">claudia82</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 6, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Easy set up and simple to use! Great result of picture optimization with direct speed - page load result, even in the free version. Works with NextGen Gallery and Facebook widgets. Helpful, fast and knowledgable support! Good job!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\