s-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tivustream\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f8b75e98cbeea46b21a428f17186ca20?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f8b75e98cbeea46b21a428f17186ca20?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tivustream\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tivustream</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">A very useful and working plugin \nUsing Free versione but really interested to upgrade deserved !</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great function</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/harvestmoonfriends\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dbcaee23d3f3c636f6de0f8bc8d1890d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dbcaee23d3f3c636f6de0f8bc8d1890d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/harvestmoonfriends\" class=\"reviewer-name\">harvestmo