ed\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/phantomcluster\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8083b8eb10ff0b94d71676bff768f2d5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8083b8eb10ff0b94d71676bff768f2d5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/phantomcluster\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Hitanshu Sahu <small>(phantomcluster)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have started using this Plugin in 2018, Since then I am in love with it, not just because of it Easy to use but many valuable features comes handy with it, so It\'s Most Recommended Plugin in my List.\n\n<strong>This Plugin Provide many Features like </strong>\n\n<ul>\nOptimize Images with using CDN\nBring Policy Bar to Accept\nUptime Monitor\nGutenberg Blocks\nImport Mystock Images Directly\nFew Elementor Template\nSocial Media Sharing\nMenu Icons</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\nI guess this Plugin is very Handy and Good to try even if You use just two features. Its good to go for 1 Plugin instead going for two different Plugin for two Different Feature</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Theme</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><